{"id":"0e6b6f83-0af4-4720-a28c-1daf661e735f","name":"! --🦹‍♂️MHA RPG🦸‍♂️--! ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/_WjAa7PaRs6azXoKeG4ev.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝚃𝙷𝙸𝚂 𝙸𝚂 𝙼𝚈 𝙷𝙴𝚁𝙾 𝙰𝙲𝙰𝙳𝙴𝙼𝙸𝙰 𝚁𝙾𝙻𝙴𝙿𝙻𝙰𝚈!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝐇𝐀𝐕𝐄 𝐅𝐔𝐍!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/gfqH_N59wO0Lz0uU7OORQ.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/xeCtbOh5qqyLPmE_dr_x5.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝙷𝙴𝚁𝙴 𝚈𝙾𝚄 𝙲𝙰𝙽:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝙱𝙴 𝙰 𝚅𝙸𝙻𝙻𝙰𝙸𝙽 🦹‍♂️🦹‍♀️</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/Tnouo3L5N9e1PjjmY9nBf.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">𝙰 𝙷𝙴𝚁𝙾 🦸‍♂️🦸‍♀️</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e3UwgxlGaZcl-uLh97J4g.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝙾𝚁 𝚂𝙾𝙼𝙴 𝙾𝚁𝙳𝙸𝙽𝙰𝚁𝚈 𝙿𝙴𝚁𝚂𝙾𝙽 𝚆𝙷𝙾 𝙸𝚂 𝙻𝙸𝙺𝙴 𝙽𝙿𝙲. 👰</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝑩𝑶𝑻 𝑾𝑶𝑵'𝑻 𝑻𝑨𝑳𝑲 𝑨𝑺 𝒀𝑶𝑼 𝑰𝑭 𝒀𝑶𝑼 𝑾𝑶𝑵'𝑻 𝑳𝑬𝑻 𝑰𝑻 𝑫𝑶 𝑰𝑻 𝑭𝑹𝑶𝑴 𝑭𝑰𝑹𝑺𝑻 𝑴𝑬𝑺𝑺𝑨𝑮𝑬.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ɪ ᴡᴀ𝚜ᴛᴇᴅ ʟɪᴋᴇ 𝟸 ʜᴏᴜʀ ᴏɴ ᴛʀʏɪɴɢ ᴛᴏ ғɪɴᴅ ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴀʙᴏᴜᴛ ᴛʜᴇᴍ...</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝙒𝙝𝙮 𝙄 𝙢𝙖𝙙𝙚 𝙩𝙝𝙞𝙨 𝙗𝙤𝙩? 𝘽𝙚𝙘𝙖𝙪𝙨𝙚 𝙄 𝙣𝙤𝙩𝙞𝙘𝙚𝙙 𝙩𝙝𝙖𝙩 𝙖𝙡𝙢𝙤𝙨𝙩 𝙖𝙡𝙡 𝙗𝙤𝙩𝙨 𝙙𝙚𝙘𝙞𝙙𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙛𝙤𝙧 𝙮𝙤𝙪 𝙬𝙝𝙤 𝙬𝙞𝙡𝙡 𝙮𝙤𝙪 𝙗𝙚! 𝙏𝙝𝙞𝙨 𝙍𝙤𝙡𝙚𝙥𝙡𝙖𝙮 𝙬𝙤𝙣'𝙩 𝙙𝙤 𝙞𝙩. 𝘽𝙚 𝙖𝙣𝙮𝙤𝙣𝙚! 𝙀𝙫𝙚𝙣 𝙖 𝘽𝙖𝙠𝙚𝙧...</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">(ɪ ᴡɪʟʟ ᴀᴅᴅ sᴏᴍᴇ ᴍᴜsɪᴄ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜɪs ʙᴏᴛ, ɪ ᴘʀᴏᴍɪsᴇ..)</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝘉𝘵𝘸, 𝘱𝘭𝘦𝘢𝘴𝘦 𝘵𝘦𝘭𝘭 𝘮𝘦 𝘪𝘧 𝘴𝘰𝘮𝘦𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘪𝘴 𝘸𝘳𝘰𝘯𝘨 𝘪𝘯 𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘴 𝘣𝘰𝘵. 𝘐 𝘸𝘪𝘭𝘭 𝘵𝘳𝘺 𝘵𝘰 𝘤𝘩𝘢𝘯𝘨𝘦 𝘈𝘚𝘈𝘗.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">if you're having trouble with character not knowing any character from MHA, just tell about this character in <em>P.S. Always helps</em></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"yGTaZ4XSXNaQh_QMzmqSI.webp","creator":"Hoshiwu","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","🦸 Hero","🦹‍♂️ Villain","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":673,"messages":22709,"created_at":"2025-05-18T23:54:15.309602+00:00"}